The technician used these materials: {{materials}}

Available team products: {{products}}

For each material, return the matching product hash ID ONCE per unit. Example: '2x Dichtung' should return ['hash1', 'hash1'], not ['hash1']. If no product matches, return an empty array.

The technician worked {{hours}} hours.

Available team services: {{services}}

Return the hourly-rate service hash ID (single item array). If no hourly rate service is configured, return an empty array.
